546
00:26:13,542 --> 00:26:15,250
Soufan:
<i>Our main goal was to see</i>

547
00:26:15,334 --> 00:26:16,626
<i>if there is
imminent threat,</i>

548
00:26:16,709 --> 00:26:20,125
so we didn't really
have time to play.

549
00:26:20,209 --> 00:26:22,626
<i>So during that conversation,
